<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Online Work Opportunity</title>

<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b0014, #1a0033);
    color: #ffffff;
}

/* Header */
header{
    text-align:center;
    padding:50px 20px;
}
header h1{
    font-size:28px;
    color:#c084fc;
}
header p{
    font-size:16px;
    opacity:0.9;
}

/* Main Card */
.container{
    max-width:900px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:20px;
}
.card{
    background:rgba(20,0,40,0.95);
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:30px;
    box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(192,132,252,0.3);
}

/* Sections */
.section{
    margin-bottom:30px;
}
.section h2{
    color:#a855f7;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}
.section p{
    line-height:1.6;
    font-size:15px;
}

/* List */
ul{
    padding-left:20px;
}
ul li{
    margin-bottom:8px;
}

/* Buttons */
.buttons{
    text-align:center;
    margin-top:30px;
}
.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin:10px;
    padding:14px 28px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#9333ea,#7c3aed);
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:30px;
    font-weight:bold;
    box-shadow:0 0 15px rgba(168,85,247,0.6);
    transition:0.3s;
}
.btn:hover{
    transform:scale(1.05);
    box-shadow:0 0 25px rgba(192,132,252,0.9);
}

/* Footer */
footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
    font-size:13px;
    opacity:0.7;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Online Network Marketing Opportunity</h1>
    <p>Work From Home • Part Time / Full Time</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <div class="card">

        <div class="section">
            <h2>About This Work</h2>
            <p>
                This is a genuine online work opportunity for people who want to earn from home.
                Freshers and non-experienced candidates can also apply.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Who Can Apply?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Age must be 18+</li>
                <li>Students / Job Seekers / Housewives</li>
                <li>Basic mobile & internet required</li>
                <li>No prior experience needed</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Income Potential</h2>
            <p>
                Earn between <b>₹15,000 – ₹30,000 per month</b> depending on your performance.
                Work at your own time with full flexibility.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="buttons">
            <a class="btn" href="https://form.svhrt.com/69689832ee61c0f2f2ab2256" target="_blank">
                Apply Now
            </a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://form.svhrt.com/69689832ee61c0f2f2ab2256" target="_blank">
                Join Today
            </a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://form.svhrt.com/69689832ee61c0f2f2ab2256" target="_blank">
                Start Online Work
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    © 2026 Online Work Platform • All Rights Reserved
</footer>

</body>
</html>
